# GitHub personal access token — READ-ONLY, public data only.
# Used server-side to query GitHub's GraphQL API for public contribution data.
#
# Create one: https://github.com/settings/tokens
#   - Fine-grained token with NO extra permissions works for public data, OR
#   - Classic token with no scopes (or just "public_repo") works too.
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and paste your token below. Never commit ".env".
GITHUB_TOKEN=
